Package tech.mcprison.prison.internal

Since Prison is cross-internal (and cross-version), the Minecraft server interfaces provided by mods like Bukkit and Sponge are not provided for us.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandSender
    Represents any entity that may send commands and receive output.
    Player
    Represents a player on the Minecraft server.
    Scheduler
    Allows tasks to be scheduled to run later or at intervals, on the server thread or on its own thread.
    World
    Represents a world on the Minecraft server.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ItemStack
    Represents an item stack.

Package tech.mcprison.prison.internal Description

Since Prison is cross-internal (and cross-version), the Minecraft server interfaces provided by mods like Bukkit and Sponge are not provided for us. Instead, we must make our own and have the implementations implement them with the different mods.
Since:
API 1.0
